g.text: The authors would like to thank the assistance given by the

The authors declare that they have no financial or personal

A.N. wrote and conceptualised the article by coming up with
the particular title. She had to do more research on the
pertinent issues of participants’ perceptions of climate change
and health hazards, and finalised the article before submitting
it to the journal. M.T. did the initial research and also
facilitated the collection of primary data. She also provided
empirical evidence through informal observations as she had
to organise the meetings with the various stakeholders in
Mount Darwin. She also applied for the ethics clearance.
